01:10.633 --> 01:12.010
♪ He's got a sleigh full ♪

01:12.176 --> 01:13.678
♪ It's not gonna stay full ♪

01:14.053 --> 01:17.265
♪ Of stuff that he's dropping
every stop of the way ♪

01:17.390 --> 01:20.393
♪ Everybody's waiting
for the man with the bag ♪

01:20.560 --> 01:23.104
♪ 'Cause Christmas
is coming again ♪

01:23.271 --> 01:25.648
♪ He'll be here... ♪

01:26.691 --> 01:30.320
